@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ovfdcd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (0.19 / 0.26)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.70 * v2 + 0.23)) / wp.cos((v0 + 0.27 + v1 + 0.66)))
    tmp = 0.82
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.98) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.98)) * ((v2 + 0.60 * v0 + 0.54) * (v0 + 0.20 - v0 + 0.13)))
    data[tid] = v0
